snippet: Andy Murray is one win away from becoming the first five-time champion at Queen's Club after he defeated fifth-seeded Marin Cilic of Croatia 6-3, 4-6, 6-3 to reach Sunday's final....
lead_paragraph: Andy Murray is one win away from becoming the first five-time champion at Queen's Club after he defeated fifth-seeded Marin Cilic of Croatia 6-3, 4-6, 6-3 to reach Sunday's final.

headline.print_headline: Murray Nears Record 5th Title, Plays Raonic in Queen's Final
headline.main: Murray Nears Record 5th Title, Plays Raonic in Queen's Final
